data.description: Absolutely exquisite home in Nixa with a great cul de sac location. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has had a complete remodel with all new flooring, kitchen with new sink, granite, faucets and an additional granite bar sitting area, 2 year old HVAC, 2 year old roof, and new bathrooms with large walk-in showers. The exterior of the home is well maintained with outside lighting features, a large privacy fended in yard with a Timbertech covered deck that spans the entire backside of the home, storage shed, hot tub that stays and an above ground pool with new liner, pump and deck.
